list.title: Iter8or#avg
list.description: Calculates the average of the elements in the iterable.

list.title: Iter8or#concat
list.description: Concatenates the current iterable with other Iter8or instances.

list.title: Iter8or#drop
list.description: Drops the first `n` elements from the iterable.

list.title: Iter8or#filter
list.description: Filters the iterable using the provided predicate function.

list.title: Iter8or#flat
list.description: Flattens the iterable up to the specified depth.

list.title: Iter8or#flatMap
list.description: Maps and flattens the iterable using the provided function.

list.title: Iter8or#map
list.description: Применяет функцию ко всем элементам итератора и возвращает новый Iter8or.

list.title: Iter8or#max
list.description: Finds the maximum value in the iterable.

list.title: Iter8or#min
list.description: Finds the minimum value in the iterable.

list.title: Iter8or#reduce
list.description: Reduces the iterable using the provided reducer function.

list.title: Iter8or#reverse
list.description: Reverses the order of the elements in the iterable.

list.title: Iter8or#sum
list.description: Sums the elements in the iterable.

list.title: Iter8or#take
list.description: Takes the first `n` elements from the iterable.

list.title: module.exports
list.description: Создает итератор, который применяет функцию ко всем элементам входного итератора.
